      "description": "Taxation without representation, the Stamp Act, Boston Tea Party, and growing colonial grievances against Britain.",
      "gradeLevel": 4,
      "standardCode": "D2.His.14.3-5",
      "strand": "revolution-founding",
      "contentDepth": "survey",
      "defaultPresentation": "intermediate"
    },
    {
      "id": "revolutionary-war",
      "name": "The Revolutionary War",
      "description": "Key battles, leaders (Washington, Jefferson, Franklin), and events from Lexington and Concord through Yorktown.",
      "gradeLevel": 4,
